Respect for the public or barrier-freeness is one thing, but only when we become important athletes, artists, actors, politicians or lawyers will things really start to change.
So far, these are isolated cases of people with strong wills.
The Tap Tap is very popular at the moment, but let's go back a few years what made you start it in 1998?
