He proposed to change this ineffective distribution. Don't let condoms be just behind counters, but the 100 can be found in dispensers in public toilets, places where young people often go.
"It's not promiscuity support.
Nor is it about "paying for beer and a motel," as Governor Emilio González responded to a question about whether he would agree to distribute condoms in his district.
There's no such thing as sexuality. It's best to make condoms available to those who are already leading a sex life," he said.
Key numbers in Jalisco
There were 13,435 cases (12,158 cases of AIDS and 1,317 cases of HIV).
This is the fourth place in new and identified AIDS cases in Mexico and 13th in HIV-related cases.
92% of infections take place through sexual channels, 6% bloodstream y 2% perinate.
